      "writtenOn": "2021-01-13T20:06:25Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Ah ok then an option is to explicitly call out that the system should strip everything after and including \";\" when filtering?\n\nThus the \";\" part should be denied here. I dunno, I\u0027m not sure I\u0027ll use this feature yet so it\u0027s not a big deal to me.",
